{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "rejox8f4vc8",
    "category": "movie",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ReJox8F4VC8",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, Leo. Let's get ready.",
      "zh": "好了，Leo。準備出發吧。",
      "ja": "よし、レオ。準備しよう。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All right, Pixie's all good to go.",
      "zh": "好了，Pixie準備好了。",
      "ja": "よし、ピクシーは準備万端だ。",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Great. Are the little gift bags in the car?",
      "zh": "太好了。小禮物袋在車上嗎？",
      "ja": "いいね。小さなギフトバッグは車にある？",
      "time": "00:00:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah, all back to it.",
      "zh": "是的，都放好了。",
      "ja": "うん、全部戻したよ。",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thanks James.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，James。",
      "ja": "ありがとう、ジェームズ。",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, off we go.",
      "zh": "好了，出發吧。",
      "ja": "よし、行こう。",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "喔。",
      "ja": "あっ。",
      "time": "00:00:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm about to do it here.",
      "zh": "我快要成功了。",
      "ja": "ここでやろうとしている。",
      "time": "00:00:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm about to do it here.",
      "zh": "我快要成功了。",
      "ja": "ここでやろうとしている。",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, hey, Kayla.",
      "zh": "喔，嗨，Kayla。",
      "ja": "ああ、やあ、ケイラ。",
      "time": "00:00:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi. I'm sorry. I'm early.",
      "zh": "嗨，抱歉，我來早了。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。ごめん、早く来ちゃった。",
      "time": "00:00:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, you're fine. I'll take you back. Come on.",
      "zh": "沒關係。我送你回去，來吧。",
      "ja": "大丈夫だよ。送ってあげる。さあ。",
      "time": "00:01:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And bring it back.",
      "zh": "然後帶回來。",
      "ja": "そして持ち帰ってね。",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Great.",
      "zh": "太好了。",
      "ja": "いいね。",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So how have the exercises been going at home?",
      "zh": "那麼，在家做運動進展如何？",
      "ja": "家での運動はどう？",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Fine.",
      "zh": "還不錯。",
      "ja": "順調だよ。",
      "time": "00:01:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How's the walking park going?",
      "zh": "散步公園怎麼樣？",
      "ja": "ウォーキングパークはどう？",
      "time": "00:01:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "還可以。",
      "ja": "まあまあだね。",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you have anyone at home to help study you? Your mom or dad?",
      "zh": "家裡有人幫你練習嗎？你媽媽或爸爸？",
      "ja": "家で誰かが勉強を手伝ってくれてる？お母さんかお父さん？",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe if we're back to Kansas.",
      "zh": "也許回堪薩斯的時候吧。",
      "ja": "多分カンザスに戻ったらね。",
      "time": "00:01:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Already?",
      "zh": "已經回去了？",
      "ja": "もう？",
      "time": "00:01:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I knew you had some quiet.",
      "zh": "我知道你有些安靜的時候。",
      "ja": "君には静かな時があるって知ってた。",
      "time": "00:01:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So who's helping you?",
      "zh": "那誰在幫你呢？",
      "ja": "じゃあ誰が手伝ってるの？",
      "time": "00:01:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can do it on my own.",
      "zh": "我可以自己做。",
      "ja": "自分でできるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What about that?",
      "zh": "那個呢？",
      "ja": "それはどう？",
      "time": "00:01:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks for having us back.",
      "zh": "謝謝你讓我們回來。",
      "ja": "また呼んでくれてありがとう。",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, we love it when you come.",
      "zh": "喔，我們很喜歡你們來。",
      "ja": "ああ、君たちが来るのは大好きだよ。",
      "time": "00:01:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh!",
      "zh": "喔！",
      "ja": "あっ！",
      "time": "00:01:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Great. The dogs are here.",
      "zh": "太好了，狗狗們來了。",
      "ja": "いいね。犬たちが来たよ。",
      "time": "00:01:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They come by every year at Christmas time.",
      "zh": "他們每年聖誕節都會來。",
      "ja": "彼らは毎年クリスマスに来るんだ。",
      "time": "00:01:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:01:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So go ahead and start on leg races,",
      "zh": "那你先開始腿部賽跑吧，",
      "ja": "じゃあ、足のレースを始めて。",
      "time": "00:01:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "and I'll get some resistance bands,",
      "zh": "我去拿一些阻力帶，",
      "ja": "私は抵抗バンドを持ってくるね。",
      "time": "00:01:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "and then I'll meet you over there.",
      "zh": "然後我會去那邊找你。",
      "ja": "それからそこで会おう。",
      "time": "00:01:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝你。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:01:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's Leo.",
      "zh": "這是Leo。",
      "ja": "これはレオだ。",
      "time": "00:01:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So this is Pixie.",
      "zh": "這是Pixie。",
      "ja": "これがピクシーだ。",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah. I want to be at her.",
      "zh": "是的。我想成為她。",
      "ja": "うん。彼女になりたい。",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I've had her for about two years now.",
      "zh": "我養她大約兩年了。",
      "ja": "彼女を飼ってもう2年になる。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Such a good boy.",
      "zh": "真是乖孩子。",
      "ja": "とてもいい子だ。",
      "time": "00:01:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So sweet.",
      "zh": "好溫柔。",
      "ja": "とても優しい。",
      "time": "00:02:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thank you for coming.",
      "zh": "謝謝你來。",
      "ja": "来てくれてありがとう。",
      "time": "00:02:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My pleasure.",
      "zh": "我的榮幸。",
      "ja": "こちらこそ。",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "喔。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Damn.",
      "zh": "該死。",
      "ja": "くそ。",
      "time": "00:02:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Merry Christmas.",
      "zh": "聖誕快樂。",
      "ja": "メリークリスマス。",
      "time": "00:02:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, thank you very much.",
      "zh": "非常感謝。",
      "ja": "どうもありがとう。",
      "time": "00:02:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hi.",
      "zh": "嗨。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:02:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is Leo.",
      "zh": "這是Leo。",
      "ja": "これはレオだ。",
      "time": "00:02:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Can we sit for a minute?",
      "zh": "我們可以坐一下嗎？",
      "ja": "ちょっと座っていい？",
      "time": "00:02:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sure.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "いいよ。",
      "time": "00:02:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I guess.",
      "zh": "我想可以。",
      "ja": "たぶんね。",
      "time": "00:02:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm Amber.",
      "zh": "我是Amber。",
      "ja": "私はアンバーです。",
      "time": "00:02:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm on Davenport Animal Haven.",
      "zh": "我在Davenport動物庇護所工作。",
      "ja": "私はダベンポート動物保護施設にいます。",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What's your name?",
      "zh": "你叫什麼名字？",
      "ja": "君の名前は？",
      "time": "00:02:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Caleb.",
      "zh": "Caleb。",
      "ja": "ケイレブ。",
      "time": "00:02:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nice to meet you, Caleb.",
      "zh": "很高興認識你，Caleb。",
      "ja": "はじめまして、ケイレブ。",
      "time": "00:02:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't worry.",
      "zh": "別擔心。",
      "ja": "心配しないで。",
      "time": "00:02:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "He's friendly.",
      "zh": "他很友善。",
      "ja": "彼は友好的だよ。",
      "time": "00:02:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, Leo.",
      "zh": "好了，Leo。",
      "ja": "よし、レオ。",
      "time": "00:02:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sit.",
      "zh": "坐下。",
      "ja": "おすわり。",
      "time": "00:02:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good boy.",
      "zh": "乖孩子。",
      "ja": "いい子だ。",
      "time": "00:02:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So can I tell you about him?",
      "zh": "我可以跟你說說他嗎？",
      "ja": "彼について話してもいい？",
      "time": "00:02:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:02:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Leo here.",
      "zh": "這是Leo。",
      "ja": "こいつがレオだ。",
      "time": "00:02:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Was that the shelter?",
      "zh": "那是在庇護所嗎？",
      "ja": "あれはシェルターだった？",
      "time": "00:02:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And when I would tidy his kennel,",
      "zh": "當我整理他的狗舍時，",
      "ja": "彼の犬舎を掃除するとき、",
      "time": "00:02:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "he'd set by my side.",
      "zh": "他會坐在我旁邊。",
      "ja": "彼は私のそばに座っていた。",
      "time": "00:02:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Just smiling and waiting.",
      "zh": "只是微笑著等待。",
      "ja": "ただ笑顔で待っていた。",
      "time": "00:02:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And then he would lick my hand afterwards.",
      "zh": "然後他會舔我的手。",
      "ja": "その後、彼は私の手を舐めた。",
      "time": "00:02:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Kind of like he was saying thanks.",
      "zh": "就像是在說謝謝。",
      "ja": "まるで感謝を伝えているようだった。",
      "time": "00:02:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And I would take him on walks.",
      "zh": "我會帶他散步。",
      "ja": "私は彼を散歩に連れて行った。",
      "time": "00:03:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And he would then look up every few steps,",
      "zh": "他每走幾步就會抬頭看我，",
      "ja": "彼は数歩ごとに私を見上げて、",
      "time": "00:03:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "like checking to see if I was as happy as he was.",
      "zh": "像是在確認我是否和他一樣快樂。",
      "ja": "私が彼と同じくらい幸せかどうかを確かめているようだった。",
      "time": "00:03:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And, you know, I wanted him to be happy all the time.",
      "zh": "我希望他一直快樂。",
      "ja": "私は彼がいつも幸せでいてほしかった。",
      "time": "00:03:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So I adopted him and ended up finding my best friend.",
      "zh": "所以我收養了他，找到了最好的朋友。",
      "ja": "だから私は彼を引き取り、最高の友達を見つけた。",
      "time": "00:03:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That sounds like you're both pretty lucky.",
      "zh": "聽起來你們都很幸運。",
      "ja": "君たちは二人ともかなり幸運だね。",
      "time": "00:03:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:03:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now he loves coming on visits and he loves Christmas.",
      "zh": "現在他喜歡來拜訪，也喜歡聖誕節。",
      "ja": "今では彼は訪問が大好きで、クリスマスも大好きだ。",
      "time": "00:03:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How can you tell?",
      "zh": "你怎麼知道？",
      "ja": "どうしてわかるの？",
      "time": "00:03:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "His tail wags more.",
      "zh": "他的尾巴搖得更多。",
      "ja": "彼の尻尾はもっとよく振れる。",
      "time": "00:03:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And he loves to take naps by the Christmas tree.",
      "zh": "他喜歡在聖誕樹旁小睡。",
      "ja": "彼はクリスマスツリーのそばで昼寝をするのが好きだ。",
      "time": "00:03:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How do you know he's not just finding a warmer spot in the wintertime?",
      "zh": "你怎麼知道他不是冬天找個暖和的地方？",
      "ja": "冬に暖かい場所を探しているだけじゃないの？",
      "time": "00:03:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Because he'll nap by the Christmas tree at my apartment",
      "zh": "因為他會在我公寓的聖誕樹旁小睡，",
      "ja": "私のアパートのクリスマスツリーのそばでも昼寝をするからだ。",
      "time": "00:03:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "and at the shelter.",
      "zh": "還有在庇護所。",
      "ja": "そしてシェルターでも。",
      "time": "00:03:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And he even moved the trees around each year,",
      "zh": "他甚至每年都會移動聖誕樹，",
      "ja": "彼は毎年ツリーを動かすことさえある。",
      "time": "00:03:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "and he always goes back to them.",
      "zh": "他總是回到那些樹旁。",
      "ja": "そしていつもそこに戻る。",
      "time": "00:03:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Quirk, he does.",
      "zh": "真是怪癖。",
      "ja": "変わった癖だね。",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是啊。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:03:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "He is.",
      "zh": "他是的。",
      "ja": "そうだよ。",
      "time": "00:03:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Fun personalities.",
      "zh": "有趣的個性。",
      "ja": "面白い性格だ。",
      "time": "00:03:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Just like us.",
      "zh": "就像我們一樣。",
      "ja": "私たちと同じだ。",
      "time": "00:03:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So do you have any fun Christmas plans?",
      "zh": "那你有什麼有趣的聖誕計劃嗎？",
      "ja": "クリスマスの楽しい予定はある？",
      "time": "00:03:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not really.",
      "zh": "沒有。",
      "ja": "特にないよ。",
      "time": "00:03:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's probably hard to focus on anything when you're working so hard to get better.",
      "zh": "當你努力康復時，很難專注於其他事情。",
      "ja": "回復に一生懸命だと、何かに集中するのは難しいよね。",
      "time": "00:03:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah, it's hard to ignore.",
      "zh": "是啊，很難忽視。",
      "ja": "そうだね、無視するのは難しい。",
      "time": "00:03:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Here.",
      "zh": "來。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:04:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Close your eyes.",
      "zh": "閉上眼睛。",
      "ja": "目を閉じて。",
      "time": "00:04:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why?",
      "zh": "為什麼？",
      "ja": "なぜ？",
      "time": "00:04:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Just try it with me.",
      "zh": "跟我一起試試看。",
      "ja": "一緒にやってみて。",
      "time": "00:04:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you one of those psychologists?",
      "zh": "你是心理學家嗎？",
      "ja": "心理学者の一人？",
      "time": "00:04:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不是。",
      "ja": "違うよ。",
      "time": "00:04:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Just a girl with a dog.",
      "zh": "只是個帶著狗的女孩。",
      "ja": "ただ犬を連れた女の子。",
      "time": "00:04:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:04:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now what?",
      "zh": "接下來呢？",
      "ja": "次は？",
      "time": "00:04:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I imagine you aren't here.",
      "zh": "想像你不在這裡。",
      "ja": "君がここにいないと想像して。",
      "time": "00:04:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nothing hurts.",
      "zh": "沒有痛楚。",
      "ja": "何も痛くない。",
      "time": "00:04:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's Christmas.",
      "zh": "是聖誕節。",
      "ja": "クリスマスだ。",
      "time": "00:04:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Where are you and what do you do?",
      "zh": "你在哪裡？在做什麼？",
      "ja": "君はどこにいて、何をしている？",
      "time": "00:04:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Where are you and what are you doing?",
      "zh": "你在哪裡？你在做什麼？",
      "ja": "君はどこにいて、何をしている？",
      "time": "00:04:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm...",
      "zh": "我在……",
      "ja": "僕は…",
      "time": "00:04:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "zh": "我不知道。",
      "ja": "わからない。",
      "time": "00:04:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Come on.",
      "zh": "來吧。",
      "ja": "さあ。",
      "time": "00:04:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There's no way you're wrong answer.",
      "zh": "不會有錯的答案。",
      "ja": "間違った答えはないよ。",
      "time": "00:04:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Fine.",
      "zh": "好吧。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:04:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm outside.",
      "zh": "我在外面。",
      "ja": "外にいる。",
      "time": "00:04:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is that it?",
      "zh": "就這樣嗎？",
      "ja": "それだけ？",
      "time": "00:04:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm still thinking.",
      "zh": "我還在想。",
      "ja": "まだ考えてる。",
      "time": "00:04:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:04:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "zh": "抱歉。",
      "ja": "ごめん。",
      "time": "00:04:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Keep going.",
      "zh": "繼續說。",
      "ja": "続けて。",
      "time": "00:04:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm on a mountain with fresh snow.",
      "zh": "我在一座覆蓋著新雪的山上。",
      "ja": "新雪の積もった山にいる。",
      "time": "00:04:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And the hair is cold, but I like it.",
      "zh": "空氣很冷，但我喜歡。",
      "ja": "空気は冷たいけど、好きだ。",
      "time": "00:04:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I'm at the top of the slope looking down.",
      "zh": "我站在坡頂往下看。",
      "ja": "斜面の頂上にいて、下を見ている。",
      "time": "00:05:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I'm ready to ski.",
      "zh": "我準備滑雪了。",
      "ja": "スキーの準備ができている。",
      "time": "00:05:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I like that.",
      "zh": "我喜歡這樣。",
      "ja": "それはいいね。",
      "time": "00:05:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So you're a skier.",
      "zh": "所以你是滑雪者。",
      "ja": "君はスキーヤーなんだね。",
      "time": "00:05:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I've been a few times, but it's more so that I'd be able to do it.",
      "zh": "我滑過幾次，但更重要的是我能做到。",
      "ja": "何度か行ったけど、できるようになりたいんだ。",
      "time": "00:05:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I wouldn't be worried about my leg being weak or scarred.",
      "zh": "我不會擔心我的腿會虛弱或有疤痕。",
      "ja": "足が弱かったり傷跡があったりするのを心配しない。",
      "time": "00:05:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Maybe one day you won't even think about it.",
      "zh": "也許有一天你甚至不會想起它。",
      "ja": "いつかはそれを考えなくなるかもね。",
      "time": "00:05:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There's more to you than your hardest days.",
      "zh": "你不只是那些艱難的日子。",
      "ja": "君は辛い日々以上の存在だ。",
      "time": "00:05:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Like what?",
      "zh": "像什麼？",
      "ja": "例えば？",
      "time": "00:05:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Like...",
      "zh": "像是……",
      "ja": "例えば…",
      "time": "00:05:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You smile.",
      "zh": "你會微笑。",
      "ja": "君は笑顔を見せる。",
      "time": "00:05:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's a great one.",
      "zh": "那是很棒的。",
      "ja": "それはいいね。",
      "time": "00:05:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "See?",
      "zh": "看吧？",
      "ja": "ほらね？",
      "time": "00:05:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't make me get out my mirror.",
      "zh": "別讓我拿出鏡子。",
      "ja": "鏡を出させないで。",
      "time": "00:05:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Please don't.",
      "zh": "拜託不要。",
      "ja": "お願い、やめて。",
      "time": "00:05:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I will take your word for it.",
      "zh": "我相信你說的。",
      "ja": "君の言葉を信じるよ。",
      "time": "00:05:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "いいね。",
      "time": "00:05:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And where would you be at Christmas?",
      "zh": "那你聖誕節會在哪裡？",
      "ja": "クリスマスはどこにいる？",
      "time": "00:05:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I would be...",
      "zh": "我會在……",
      "ja": "僕は…",
      "time": "00:05:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "and set a cozy cabin.",
      "zh": "在一間舒適的小屋裡。",
      "ja": "居心地の良い小屋にいる。",
      "time": "00:05:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Setting by a warm fire.",
      "zh": "坐在溫暖的火爐旁。",
      "ja": "暖炉のそばに座っている。",
      "time": "00:05:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I'd be painting.",
      "zh": "我會在畫畫。",
      "ja": "絵を描いている。",
      "time": "00:05:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And what's the painting of?",
      "zh": "畫的是什麼？",
      "ja": "何の絵？",
      "time": "00:05:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うーん。",
      "time": "00:05:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Leo, not been by a Christmas tree.",
      "zh": "Leo，沒在聖誕樹旁。",
      "ja": "レオ、クリスマスツリーのそばじゃないよ。",
      "time": "00:05:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you an artist?",
      "zh": "你是藝術家嗎？",
      "ja": "君はアーティスト？",
      "time": "00:06:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不是。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:06:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe if things were different,",
      "zh": "也許如果情況不同，",
      "ja": "もし状況が違えば、",
      "time": "00:06:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "but I'm doing what I need to do right now.",
      "zh": "但我現在做我需要做的事。",
      "ja": "でも今は必要なことをしている。",
      "time": "00:06:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I do paint for fun every now and then,",
      "zh": "我偶爾會畫畫當作娛樂，",
      "ja": "時々趣味で絵を描くよ。",
      "time": "00:06:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "one at a time.",
      "zh": "一次一幅。",
      "ja": "一度に一枚ずつ。",
      "time": "00:06:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, I'd like to see that painting.",
      "zh": "我想看看那幅畫。",
      "ja": "その絵を見たいな。",
      "time": "00:06:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Really?",
      "zh": "真的嗎？",
      "ja": "本当に？",
      "time": "00:06:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, if I do it, you'll have to stop by the shelter to see it.",
      "zh": "如果我畫了，你得來庇護所看看。",
      "ja": "もし描いたら、シェルターに見に来てね。",
      "time": "00:06:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You'd hang it up there?",
      "zh": "你會掛在那裡？",
      "ja": "そこに飾るの？",
      "time": "00:06:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sure.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "もちろん。",
      "time": "00:06:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "At least at Christmas time.",
      "zh": "至少聖誕節期間。",
      "ja": "少なくともクリスマスの時期はね。",
      "time": "00:06:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey there.",
      "zh": "嗨。",
      "ja": "やあ。",
      "time": "00:06:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello.",
      "zh": "你好。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:06:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, I guess I should stop disturbing you.",
      "zh": "我想我該不打擾你了。",
      "ja": "邪魔しないほうがいいね。",
      "time": "00:06:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝你。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:06:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I mean, for stopping by, not for disturbing me.",
      "zh": "我是說，謝謝你來，不是打擾我。",
      "ja": "来てくれてありがとう、邪魔じゃないよ。",
      "time": "00:06:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm glad we got a chat.",
      "zh": "很高興我們聊了聊。",
      "ja": "話せてよかった。",
      "time": "00:06:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Anytime you want to say hi to Leo,",
      "zh": "隨時想跟Leo打招呼，",
      "ja": "レオに会いたい時はいつでも、",
      "time": "00:06:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "or me, the other animals,",
      "zh": "或是我和其他動物，",
      "ja": "私や他の動物にも、",
      "time": "00:06:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "stop by the shelter.",
      "zh": "來庇護所看看。",
      "ja": "シェルターに立ち寄ってね。",
      "time": "00:06:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:06:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝你。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:06:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Merry Christmas, Caleb.",
      "zh": "聖誕快樂，Caleb。",
      "ja": "メリークリスマス、ケイレブ。",
      "time": "00:06:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Merry Christmas.",
      "zh": "聖誕快樂。",
      "ja": "メリークリスマス。",
      "time": "00:06:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Come on, Leo.",
      "zh": "來吧，Leo。",
      "ja": "さあ、レオ。",
      "time": "00:06:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好吧。",
      "ja": "よし。",
      "time": "00:06:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The red one, not the more of the purple one.",
      "zh": "紅色的，不是紫色的。",
      "ja": "赤いの、紫じゃなくて。",
      "time": "00:07:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you so much faster.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，快多了。",
      "ja": "ありがとう、とても速いね。",
      "time": "00:07:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You take care.",
      "zh": "保重。",
      "ja": "気をつけて。",
      "time": "00:07:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "See you soon.",
      "zh": "再見。",
      "ja": "またね。",
      "time": "00:07:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Bye.",
      "zh": "拜拜。",
      "ja": "バイバイ。",
      "time": "00:07:17"
    }
  ]
}